# 卷积神经网络研究综述（周飞燕等）

## 下载

### Docker

```
docker pull apachecn0/juanji-shenjingwangluo-yanjiu-zongshu-zhoufeiyan-deng
docker run -tid -p <port>:80 apachecn0/juanji-shenjingwangluo-yanjiu-zongshu-zhoufeiyan-deng
# 访问 http://localhost:{port} 查看文档
```

### PYPI

```
pip install juanji-shenjingwangluo-yanjiu-zongshu-zhoufeiyan-deng
juanji-shenjingwangluo-yanjiu-zongshu-zhoufeiyan-deng <port>
# 访问 http://localhost:{port} 查看文档
```

### NPM

```
npm install -g juanji-shenjingwangluo-yanjiu-zongshu-zhoufeiyan-deng
juanji-shenjingwangluo-yanjiu-zongshu-zhoufeiyan-deng <port>
# 访问 http://localhost:{port} 查看文档
```
